==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pointless
<hw>Point"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no point; blunt; wanting keenness; obtuse; <as>as, a <ex>pointless</ex> sword; a <ex>pointless</ex> remark.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Blunt; obtuse, dull; stupid.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pointlessly</ent>⟦br⟧
